                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "The causeway is a straight line and you are the only thing moving on it. Of course I saw you. I scout the crossing so the ones nearly done reach the ones who decide it whole."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Past the far arch wait the Royal League and the Battle Frontier. I test the crossing - decline if you must, the fee is the toll for a free pass."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Frontier Causeway. Nowhere to not be seen on a straight run like this. Battle me or pay the crossing fee and walk on - the League is past the arch either way."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Four hundred crossings logged this season. Three were interesting. You are about to tell me which column you belong in."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The chronicler at the arch writes down what you did. I only care what you do in the next six minutes. Between us we have the whole of you covered."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Frontier Scout Rhea",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
